BSD joystick code should be compatible with 'old' Linux joystick
driver, add some code to make this work (e.g. use BSD joystick
handling code, but include <system/joystick.h>)

Moreover, make from OpenBSD is not the GNU make. You need to add two
implicits rules: 
joyreadbutton: joyreadbutton.o
joyreadaxis: joyreadaxis.o

